This directory stores the chest X-ray dataset.

Files in this directory are git-ignored (large dataset files).

Expected structure:
    data/chest_xrays/
    ├── train/
    │   ├── NORMAL/
    │   └── PNEUMONIA/
    ├── val/
    │   ├── NORMAL/
    │   └── PNEUMONIA/
    └── test/
        ├── NORMAL/
        └── PNEUMONIA/

Download:
    python scripts/download_dataset.py

Or manually from:
    https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/paultimothymooney/chest-xray-pneumonia
